  <brief_title>Effect of Galactooligosaccharides on Incidence of Atopic Manifestations in Infants</brief_title>
  <official_title>Double Blind, Randomised Study on the Effect of Prebiotics on Incidence of Atopic Manifestations in Infants</official_title>
  <sponsors>
