  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Addition of prebiotic galactooligosaccharides to hypoallergenic starter formula would lead to
      decreased allergic (atopic) symptoms in nonbreastfed infants with a positive history of
      allergy in family
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
